data.description: Enjoy privacy in 2011 Champion 3BR-2BA, 1,980SF on 20 forested acres w/Haden Creek frontage. Serene Moses Mtns & territorial views. Formal front living room w/wood burning fireplace+family room. Large eat in kitchen w/island, breakfast bar&nook+formal dining area. Massive mud room. Beautiful 5pc master en suite w/split bedrooms. Mostly fenced/cross fenced w/barn/shed for livestock options. Approx 7.4 miles off Disautel/Hwy 155 & 5 miles to Crawfish Lake on county maintained roads. No CCR's here!
